name: Luggage Tags Save the Dates - any color
description:
>>>>>This listing is for the custom design fee/deposit for these Luggage Tag Save the Dates ONLY and does NOT pay for printing, assembly and shipping<<<<<

Perfect for destination weddings, beach weddings, bridal showers and engagement parties.

* All of the colors, clip-art, maps and text can be changed based on your location and needs (cruise ship, flowers, starfish etc.)
* Minimum order is 30 but you can order any number of Luggage Tags beyond 30
* Luggage Tags are die cut on the corners and fully assembled with raffia string or baker's twine.

[ DETAILS ]

Luggage Tag Save the Dates are $1.95 each, minimum order is 30 tags
SIZE: 3.5 x 5 (8.9 x 12.7 cm)
PAPER: Premium 130 lbs Recycled Paper (100% post-consumer material)
ENVELOPES: White or cream colored 4bar sized envelopes with a square flap
COLOR OPTIONS: Choose your color from the color chart or custom. Colors on main image are: watermelon, aqua, tangerine

[ UPGRADE OPTIONS ]

Colored envelopes: $0.75 each
Return address printing (+ $0.50 per envelope)
Additional white or cream envelopes: $0.25 each (all sizes, minimum of 5 each)

[ CUSTOMIZATION, PROOFING and TURNAROUND ]

When you purchase this listing, please indicate the number of Luggage Tags you would like to order in the note to seller section during checkout then I will set up an invoice for you where you can provide me with all your wedding details to be included.

Within 2 days of receiving payment for the Luggage Tags, I will email a digital proof of your design. Once you receive the digital proof, you will be able to make up to TWO free changes - additional changes beyond that will have a fee of $10 per change. Changes may include color change, font changes, type, etc. Once you approve the design, I will move ahead and print the tags.

They will ship within 7 business days after final approval is granted. Please keep in mind that I will not print your order until you have given approval, so look over proofs promptly and carefully

Color may vary slightly between what you see on the monitor and the final printed product based on different monitor calibrations.

[ SHIPPING ]

- All orders generally ship via Priority Mail within US or US First Class international mail

name: Heart Address Stamp for Save the Dates & Wedding Invitations with your date and initials
description:
Add your return address in style with these cute customized rubber address stamps. Featuring a heart design with your address, initials and wedding date. Use as an address stamp as well as decoration for all your mailings. Also available with a plain heart in the center without the initials or wedding date.

[ITEM DETAILS]

Rubber address stamp with Classic Wooden Handle
Imprint size 1.5 "x 1.5"
Design is personalized with your initials, wedding date and address
Also available as a self inking stamp for $35.00 in 5 colors - please contact me for details


[HOW TO ORDER]

1) Include your date//names//address in the note to seller section during checkout. Please write your names, address and date *exactly* as you wish it to appear on the stamp.

2) Within 24 hours of placing your order, you will receive a digital proof of your design with the information you provided. Once you receive the digital proof, you will be able to make one free change - additional changes beyond that will have a fee of $5 per change.

3) Once you approve your design, your custom stamp will be created within 2 business days

[ SHIPPING ]

- All orders ship via USPS First Class Mail (1-6 business days)
- Expedited shipping is available
